VI want you to reimagine how life is organized on earth.
p4
aVThink of the planet like a human body that we inhabit.
p5
aVThe skeleton is the transportation system of roads and railways,
p6
aVbridges and tunnels, air and seaports
p7
aVthat enable our mobility across the continents.
p8
aVThe vascular system that powers the body
p9
aVare the oil and gas pipelines and electricity grids.
p10
aVthat distribute energy.
p11
aVAnd the nervous system of communications
p12
aVis the Internet cables, satellites, cellular networks
p13
aVand data centers that allow us to share information.
