aa(lp89
VNow let's stop and think about it for a minute.
p90
aVSpending so much more on building the foundations of global society
p91
aVrather than on the tools to destroy it
p92
aVcan have profound consequences.
p93
aVConnectivity is how we optimize the distribution
p94
aVof people and resources around the world.
p95
aVIt is how mankind comes to be more than just the sum of its parts.
p96
aVI believe that is what is happening.
